cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel approach for few-shot learning using meta-learning and transfer learning with deep neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing tasks, which could place it in cs.CL (Computation and Language) and the use of deep neural networks suggests cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible sub-category.
